Thank you for participanting in our experiment again! You will be asked to play the Dysfunctional Ball Game again. We will briefly recap the rules before we start.

Press Next to continue.

Thank you for closing all other tabs.

We will now invite you to fill in some questionnaires, before starting the game.
This will take about 5 minutes.

Press the Next button to continue.

In the following, we will perform a baseline assessment. This means that we will ask you a few questions relating to your experiences over the past month.

Press the Next button to continue.

Thank you for your answers! Now we will ask you a few more questions relating to your feelings in the last 24 hours.

Press the Next button to continue.
